Program: Crossing Continents
Title: Pakistan Drugs
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00p315w
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 7 Dec 2009
Julia Rooke accompanies former heroin dealer, Urfan Azad, on a journey back to the remote mountain madrassa in north west Pakistan where he received drugs rehabilitation and spiritual healing. But during their journey Urfan reveals how young recovering addicts and criminals were given military training and that some went on to fight in Afghanistan. Show less